# Social Media Checklist for College Students

## ✅ Do's
- Think before you post—consider how it may affect your reputation.
- Keep your profiles professional and appropriate.
- Respect others’ opinions and communicate politely.
- Protect your privacy by adjusting security settings.
- Verify information before sharing to avoid spreading misinformation.

## ❌ Don'ts
- Don’t share personal or sensitive information publicly.
- Don’t engage in online arguments or cyberbullying.
- Don’t post inappropriate or offensive content.
- Don’t overshare details about your daily life or location.
